  <http://example.com/ns#s> <http://example.com/ns#p> ?g_115 .
  ?e_bnode <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#reifies> <<( <http://example.com/ns#s> <http://example.com/ns#p> ?g_115 )>> .
